# Radicale CardDAV Server

A lightweight CardDAV server that syncs contacts from Supabase to your devices.

## Features
- Reads contacts from Supabase via REST API
- Real-time sync with iOS, Android, macOS, Thunderbird
- Row Level Security for safe API access
- No local storage - all data from Supabase

## Quick Start
See [README.md](README.md) for full deployment instructions.

## Environment Variables Required
- `SUPABASE_URL`
- `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`
